quran[71]{c,v,t}:
  80,1,"A busa lifahleho, a furalla"
  80,2,Hobane ho ile ha tla monna oa sefofu ho eena
  80,3,Empa ke`ng se neng se ka u bolella hore mohlaope a ka hola
  80,4,"Kapa ho amohela temoso, le thuto ea mo atlehisa"
  80,5,Ha ele ea hopolang hore eena o ea ikhona
  80,6,Eena o mo thehela tsebe
  80,7,Le ha e le hore ha se molato oa hao ha a sa hole
  80,8,Empa haele ea tlileng ho uena ka boitelo
  80,9,Le ka ts’abo
  80,10,Ha u oa ka oa mo natsa
  80,11,Ruri sena ke temoso
  80,12,"Kahoo, lesa ea ratang ho e amohela, a e boloke khopolong"
  80,13,Kahar’a mangolo e ea hlompheha (al-lauh al-mahfuz)
  80,14,E phahame e hloekile e ea halalela
  80,15,Ka matsoho a bangoli
  80,16,"Ba hlomphehang ba hloekileng, ba toka"
  80,17,"Sekhobo se be ho motho, ke eng se entseng hore a latole Allah"
  80,18,O hlotsoe ka eng
  80,19,"Ka lerotholi la there: U mo hlotse, A mo matlafatsa ka hohle"
  80,20,Eaba U mo nolofaletsa tsela
  80,21,"A mo hlophela lefu, le ho patoa lebitleng"
  80,22,"Ka thato Ea Hae, U tla mo tsosa"
  80,23,Ha a phethisa seo Allah A mo laetseng sona
  80,24,Motho ha a ke a lemohe lijo tsa hae
  80,25,Kamoo Re nesang pula kateng
  80,26,Re petsolang lefats’e
  80,27,Re melisa lijo-thollo holim’a lona
  80,28,"Morara, le lijo tse ahang ‘mele"
  80,29,Mehloare le lipalema
  80,30,Le lirapa tse hlehleaneng ka lifate
  80,31,Le litholoana le lesere
  80,32,Ele nala molemong oa lona le mehlape
  80,33,Khabareng e tlare ho utloahala molumo o tabolang meropa ea tsebe
  80,34,Letsatsing leo motho a tla baleha ngoana’a bo
  80,35,‘Mae le ntata’e
  80,36,Mosali le bana ba hae
  80,37,"E mong le e mong letsatsing leo, o tla be a na le mats`enyeho a lekaneng ho tsotella e mong"
  80,38,"Letsatsing leo, lifahleho tse ling li tla ela"
  80,39,"Li ts’eha, li nyakalletse"
  80,40,Lifahleho tse ling tsona letsatsing leo li tla pulufala
  80,41,Li apareloe ke lefifi
  80,42,"Bao e tlabe e le balatoli ba Allah, baetsi ba tse mpe"
  81,1,Mohla letsatsi le timelang
  81,2,"Linaleli li oelang, li fifala"
  81,3,Lithaba li nyamela
  81,4,Li kamele tse ts`ehali tse emereng likhoeli li le leshome li lahluoe feela
  81,5,Liphoofolo tse hlaha li bokelloang ‘moho
  81,6,Mohla maoatle a belang
  81,7,Mephefomoloho e kopang’oang
  81,8,"Mohla lesea la ngoanana le tsetetsoeng le phela, le hlongoang lipotso –"
  81,9,Na u bolaetsoe sebe sefe
  81,10,Maqephe a manolloang
  81,11,Leholimo le arohang ka lehare
  81,12,Khanare ea mollo e qhomeletsoa
  81,13,Serapa se atametsoang haufinyane
  81,14,Phefomoloho ka ng`oe e tla tseba seo e se sebelelitseng
  81,15,Ruri ke bitsa ho linaleli ho paka
  81,16,"Topa, kapa ipate"
  81,17,Le ka bosiu ha bo esa
  81,18,Le ka meso ha e tebela lefifi
  81,19,Ruri! Lena ke lentsoe la morumuoa ea hlomphehang
  81,20,"Ea sitsitsoeng ka matla, le maemo kapel’a Mong`a Terone"
  81,21,"Ea hlonephehang, ea ts’epahalang"
  81,22,Molekane oa lona ha se lehlanya
  81,23,Ka ntle ho qeaqeo u ile a `monela sebakana
  81,24,Ha a pate tsebo ea tse sa bonoeng (li-jinn) ka soele
  81,25,Lena ha se lentsoe la Satane ea rohakehileng
  81,26,"Joale, le ea kae"
  81,27,Ruri ona ke molaetsa ho mafats`e ohle
  81,28,Molemong oa e mong le e mong oa lona ea ratang ho tsamaea ka nepo
  81,29,"Empa ha ho kamoo le ka ratang kantle ho thato ea Allah, – Allah `Maballi oa mafats`e. Ka lebitso la alla, Ea Lereko, Mong`a hao"